title: All 32 - Seattle Seahawks: Russell Wilson is ready to cook, but is the team? with Joe Fann (Football 6/26)
description:
For someone who has never received a vote for the award, Russell Wilson sure is getting a lot of preseason MVP buzz. Joe Fann of NBC Sports Northwest joins Will Brinson to break down why Russ deserves that recognition (2:00). They also chat about the offense around him, his desire for stars and more outspoken approach this offseason. Will Jadeveon Clowney be back for a second season with the Seahawks (11:00)? Don't count out that possibility just yet. Seattle is always a contender with Wilson at QB, but how serious of a contender will they be in 2020 (16:00)? The answers on 'All 32'.
